<br />
<br /><a href="http://www.zyx.com/chrisc/creations.html" class="postlink">http://www.zyx.com/chrisc/creations.html</a>
<br />
<br />According to that, you should be able to get the waveform from a memory dump at $4040-$407F.

		

		</td>
